    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Rise and shine! Before you begin\u2026</strong></p><p>Skim through these steps and get all your equipment ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Once done, simply dig in or wrap up ready for your day!</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00baC/ 180\u00baC (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong> lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Slice your <strong>green chilli[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Tip: Not a fan of spice? Remove the seeds!</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>When the bacon is almost ready, add your<strong> naan[s]</strong> to a separate baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 3 min or until the bread is hot</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Spread your <strong>soft cheese</strong> over the <strong>warmed naan[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drizzle over your <strong>red chilli relish</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy bacon</strong> over the soft cheese and red chilli relish naan</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/breakfast-bacon-naan-with-red-chilli-relish-and-mango-lassi/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>breakfast bacon naan with red chilli relish</strong></p><p>Serve your <strong>mango lassi </strong>to the side</p><p>Once done, simply dig in or wrap up ready for your day!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
